      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "\u0060read photo.png, write to %photo%\u0060 builds with %photo% type=image kind=png. The action\nBuild resolves the extension to the high-level type (image); the type Build supplies\nthe kind (png). Runtime: file.read.Run() returns a Data tagged Type=\u0022image\u0022 carrying\nan image.@this(bytes, mime=\u0022image/png\u0022).",
